Entries.default:
"EH! AVAST, GROUNDFILTH! WHY DISTURB LORD ADMIRAL EH, EH!?"

The imp glances left and right with evident anxiety.

"EH! NO! NO INTERRUPTIONS TO THE PLAN! LORD ADMIRAL'S WORK TOO IMPORTANT!" 

The xaurips raise their claws to block out the sound of the imp's voice.
"MUST KEEP MORALE HIGH! NO SINK BOAT THIS TIME, EH!"

"NOT DOING ANYTHING WRONG! EH! GO AWAY!" 

The xaurips flanking the imp chitter to themselves and glance around the district.
"You wouldn't be trying to steal a boat, would you?"

"G-GET HIM, CULLIES!"

The imp points at you and screeches at the top of its lungs.

Entries.default:
"BOAT? EH! LORD ADMIRAL HAS FLEET - BLAST FILTHY GROUNDSTINK CITY! START WITH YOU, EH!?" 

The pitch of the imp's voice begins to turn heads.
